<div class="individual-homepage-experience-section">
  <div class="container text-center inline-up show-on-scroll homepage-experiences">
         <h1 class="text-uppercase eyebrow-dark experience-eyebrow-mobile mb-0">Address Hotels + Resorts</h1>
              <h2 class="display-1-72 font-56-mobile experience-section-title">A Tale of Homegrown Luxury</h2>
          <p class="m-auto body-2 py-lg-0">In the elegant embrace of Address Hotels + Resorts, every chapter is infused with deeper meaning and the story is one that only you narrate. Whether you’re celebrating a romance, creating new beginnings, or simply escaping to indulge in tranquillity, we introduce the perfect setting for moments that matter most — Where Life Happens.</p>
      </div>

  
  <div id="dine-carousel">
    <div class="main-carousel" data-flickity='{ "cellAlign": "center", "contain": true,"pageDots": false }'>
          </div>
  </div>
</div>
