<div class="download-bbe-app-block spa-and-wellness-section text-center px-lg-0">
  <div class="container m-auto row no-gutters align-items-center text-center justify-content-between">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 content-box">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                  <img src=https://www.addresshotels.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/logo-black.svg alt="" class="logo">
              </div>

              <h6 class="eyebrow-dark text-center mb-0">Earn and redeem</h6>
      
              <h2 class="display-1-56 text-center ubyemaar-title-mobile mt-4 mb-0">
          Download U by Emaar App</h2>
      
      <div
        class="d-flex justify-content-center d-block d-lg-none mobile-image-container download-bbe-aspect-ratio">
                  <img width="582" height="437" decoding="async" src="https://www-addresshotels-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pixel-7a-1.jpg.webp" alt="Download U by Emaar Loyalty Program App" class="img-fluid mobile-image">
              </div>

              <p class="body-2 text-center mt-2">Elevate your stays with <strong>U by Emaar </strong>— this world-class loyalty program offers a gateway to a universe of extraordinary experiences. Seamlessly blending the finest in hospitality, leisure, and retail, this programme allows you to earn Upoints and redeem them across Emaar's exclusive portfolio. From luxurious stays at award-winning destinations to exquisite dining at renowned restaurants and unforgettable adventures at premier attractions, unlock perks that exceed your greatest expectations and indulge in only the finest.</p>
      
